			o cnEcWinBitBlt
			o cnEcWinCreateCompatibleBitmap
			o cnEcWinCreateCompatibleDC
			o cnEcWinCreateFontA
			o cnEcWinCreateFontW
			o cnEcWinCreatePen
			o cnEcWinDeleteDC
			o cnEcWinDeleteObject
			o cnEcWinGetDeviceCaps
			o cnEcWinLineTo
			o cnEcWinMoveToEx
			o cnEcWinSelectObject
			o cnEcWinSetBkColor
			o cnEcWinSetTextColor
		
		Added the following External Function to the Kernel32 Library:		cnwdad1 05/01/2002
		
			o cnEcWinMulDiv
		
		Added the following External Functions to the User32 Library:		cnwdad1 05/01/2002
		
			o cnEcWinDrawTextExA
			o cnEcWinDrawTextExW
			o cnEcWinGetDC
			o cnEcWinReleaseDC
		
		Added the following two classes:									cnwdad1 05/01/2002
		
			o CnEcRateGraph
			o CnEcRateGraphDriver
		
		Together, these classes provide a Custom Control (CnEcRateGraph) to chart the
		progress of a fluctuating value.
		
		The BaseSchema::getSingleton() method used to use the following		cnwdad1 06/01/2001
		two methods:
		
			o Object::cnEcTransactionBegin
			o Object::cnEcTransactionCommit
		
		Changed this method to handle the transaction state itself because the above
		two methods have been removed from BaseSchema.
		
		Added the following two methods to the TimeStamp Primitive:			cnwdad1 07/02/2002
		
			o cnEcShortFullFormat():String;
			o cnEcShortPartFormat():String;
		
		These methods will return the receiver with the date and time in a short
		format.
		
		Renamed the ExplicitInverseRef::getInverses method to				cnwdad1 12/01/2002
		ExplicitInverseRef::cnEcGetInverses.
		
		Renamed the Object::exceptionDetails method to Object::				cnwdad1 12/01/2002
		cnEcExceptionDetails.
		
		Removed the following properties from the BaseSchema (app) class:	cnwdad1 12/01/2002
		
			o ecStopWatch
			o myTerminalConnection
		
		Removed the following methods from the BaseSchema (app) class:		cnwdad1 12/01/2002
		
			o cnEcTimerEnd
			o cnEcTimerGo
			o exitSerialTerminal
			o initSerialTerminal
			o setMyTerminalConnection
		
		Removed the following properties from the Global class:				cnwdad1 12/01/2002
		
			o mySearchIndex
			o mySearchIndexRoot
		
		Removed the folowing methods from the Global class:					cnwdad1 12/01/2002
		
			o cnEcFileFind
			o cnEcFileSearchException
			o cnEcFileSearchFolder
			o cnEcSetSearchIndex
			o cnEcSetSearchIndexRoot
			o ecWriteServerFile
			o initSimpleSearchIndex
		
		Removed the following classes:										cnwdad1 12/01/2002
		
			o CnEcCollectionListBox
			o CnEcCollListBoxVScrollBar
			o CnEcEventsFile
			o CnEcFileSearchForm
			o CnEcGetFilePath
			o CnEcLogFileLocal
			o CnEcLogFileServer
