02200 - 02399	HCSsetupWizard
02400 - 02599	IniEditor
02600 - 02799	JDBrowser
02800 - 02999	XMLUtility
03000 - 03999	Word Dictionary/Spell Checker

BaseSchema Components
=====================
10000 - 11999	CnEcAgent
12000 - 13999	CnEcBaseEntity (general)
14000 - 15999	CnEcDataValue
16000 - 16999	CnEcLincSystemEntities
17000 - 18999	CnEcReportEntity
19000 - 19999	CnEcSerialInterface
20000 - 20999	CnEcSortEntity
21000 - 21999	CnEcXML
22000 - 23999	CnEcHtmlEntity

JADE Entities
=============
70000 - 71999	Application class
72000 - 73999	Collection classes
74000 - 75999	Connection classes
76000 - 77999	Control classes
78000 - 78999	Exception class
79000 - 79999	FileNode classes
